'''''Kill or Be Killed''''' (bwa mbere yasohokeye muri [[Amerika]] nka '''''Karate Killer''''' irongera isohorerwa muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'epfo nka  '''''Karate Olympiad''''' <ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/kill_or_be_killed</ref>) ni filime yasohotse muri 1977 muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo / [[Amerika]] karate film iyoborwa na Ivan Hall. Iyi filime yakorewe muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo<ref>https://ondemand.drafthouse.com/film/kill-or-be-killed/</ref>, iyi filime yiswe ''Kill cyangwa Be Killed'' muri [[Amerika]] mu 1980 kugira ngo yunguke menshi mu gukina filime z'ubuhanzi bw'intambara zo muri [[Amerika]].<ref>https://www.moviemeter.nl/film/56295</ref> Urukurikirane rwo kwamamara rugaragaza imiterere ya James Ryan Steve Hunt agerageza gukinira ikipe ya von Rudloff kandi ubwamamare burenze umubiri wa Ryan ahantu hose, usibye izina rya film<ref>https://www.filmiclub.com/movie/kill-or-be-killed-1980-english-movie</ref>. 

