== karate yo mubuyapani ==
Uburyo bwo kurwana muri film bwerekana uburyo bwiza bwa karate yu [[Buyapani]], tubikesha Ishyirahamwe rya Karate [[Ubuyapani|ry’Ubuyapani]] ([[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] yepfo)<ref>http://nummtheory.blogspot.com/2019/01/kill-or-be-killed-1980-kill-and-kill.html</ref>. Shihans Stan Schmidt na Norman Robinson bakoze choreografi ya karate ya firime, ndetse banagaragara muri iyi filime nk'abanyamuryango babiri bagize ikipe ya karate ya von Rudloff<ref>https://www.poemofquotes.com/quotes/film-tv/kill-or-be-killed-1980-film-quotes</ref>.
